{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9e532f74eb","title":"接见军队领导干部时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d604f3b0dc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"9e532f74eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8f86563833","type":"title","text":"接见军队领导干部时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"53faaa877d","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕闹，闹得越大、越长，越好。七闹八闹，总会闹出名堂来的，可以闹清楚。不管怎么闹，不要怕，越怕鬼越来。但也不要开枪，什么时候开枪也是不好的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"4b510b3db3","type":"paragraph","text":"全国大闹不可能。哪里有膝包，有细菌，总要爆发的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"b97503a16a","type":"paragraph","text":"南京街上闹得很厉害，我越看越高兴。闹得第三派那么多人反对内战，反对武斗，这很好嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"f297a65e7b","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥：有人讲第三派是走第三条道路的。）","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"9494db6e85","type":"paragraph","text":"哪有什么第三条道路呀，人家要大联合、大批判。你要诱导嘛！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb"}],"page":{"id":"e674260fb6","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"9e532f74eb","start":542,"end":542}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"428b7861a3","type":"paragraph","text":"全国大闹不可能。那里有脓包，有细菌，总要爆发的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"965eec1f7a","type":"title","text":"接见军队领导干部时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"a76578a6c6","type":"paragraph","text":"南京街上闹得很厉害，我越看越高兴。闹得第三派那么多人，反对内战，反对武斗，这很好嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"b4461ee041","type":"paragraph","text":"哪有什么第三条道路呀，人家要大联合，大批判。你要诱导嘛！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"bf51a1741c","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥。有人讲第三派是走第三条道路的。）","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb"},{"id":"cd886cd0c4","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕闹，闹得越大、越长，越好。七闹八闹，总会闹出名堂来的，可以闹清楚。不管怎么闹，不要怕，越怕鬼越来。但也不要开枪，什么时候开枪也是不好的。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb"}],"page":{"id":"1d36feb8d6","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9e532f74eb","start":615,"end":615}}}},"__N_SSG":true}